---
title: Salmon in Creamy Mustard Curry with green peas and rice
description: This salmon curry gets its hint of heat from mustard and its creaminess from coconut milk. Mustard is a familiar flavour in Indian cuisine, as mustard seeds are often used to imbue depth and flavour into dishes.
